(WebCore::RenderSVGInline::removeChild):
* rendering/svg/RenderSVGText.cpp:
(WebCore::RenderSVGText::subtreeChildWasAdded):
(WebCore::RenderSVGText::subtreeChildWillBeRemoved):
(WebCore::RenderSVGText::removeChild):
